'''foe''' 是一個用來描述[[超新星|超新星]]所釋出[[能量|能量]]的單位，其值為10<sup>44</sup>[[焦耳|焦耳]]或10<sup>51</sup>[[erg|erg]]。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Hartmann DH |title=Afterglows from the largest explosions in the universe |journal=Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U.S.A. |volume=96 |issue=9 |pages=4752–5 |date=April 1999 |pmid=10220364 |doi=10.1073/pnas.96.9.4752 |url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=10220364 |bibcode=1999PNAS...96.4752H |pmc=33568 |access-date=2016-11-30 |archive-date=2019-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211135214/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=10220364 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一個 '''bethe (B)''' 和一個 foe 等值。<ref name=PhysWorld-19(2)17-BetheUnit> {{cite journal |doi= 10.1088/2058-7058/19/2/31 |title= A Bethe unit |author= Stephen Weinberg |journal= Physics World |volume= 19 |number= 2 |year= 2006 }} </ref>

foe 是 [ten to the power of] '''f'''ifty-'''o'''ne '''e'''rgs<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://library.lanl.gov/cgi-bin/getfile?25-14.pdf
|format=PDF
|title=Neutrinos and Supernovae
|author1=Marc Herant
|author2=Stirling A. Colgate
|author3=Willy Benz
|author4=Chris Fryer
|date=October 25, 1997
|work=Los Alamos Sciences
